@graph.name: Olive & June Nail Art Stickers - Everyday Bouquet
@graph.description: Olive & June nail art stickers make fun manis so easy! Choose one or a full bouquet for a full-on floral look. Inspired by the most loved manicure designs from our Los Angeles salons, each sticker is hand-screened with ink that won't blur or fade. Choose your favorite sticker for an accent nail, mix-and-match for a unique look, or cover up chipped polish in a pinch. Our nail art stickers make it easy for everyone to have a beautiful nail art mani wherever you are.

review.description: The design of these nail art stickers is SO cute and I absolutely love the floral prints! However, when I tried to actually use the stickers, they were so hard to get off the paper and when I was able to get a couple off the paper, they all ripped :( Love the concept and the design, was unhappy with the ease of use.
review.author: Allison
review.name: Cute Design, Hard to Use

review.description: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Stickers broke apart as I gently tried to get them off clear paper The ones I managed to get on and apply top coat came off in 2 day ☹️
review.author: Huldeana L.
review.name: My experience

review.description: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Love these flowers. They are super cute, easy to use and I like the variety the pack has.
